{"tid":1804930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（救手足）有中國手足比狗拉左","createTime":"2019-12-31T10:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T13:21:39.000Z","uid":130419,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa7cb8bdd5104336e8a35552c8c2ffc2c09b70f","tid":1804930,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"被控擾亂秩序、襲擊警員 XY 八青年獲准保釋 一為內地大學生<br />\n<br />\n【立場】有人於上周六（28日）發起在上水廣場「北區和你 shop」，警方拘捕 20 人， 繼一名 16 歲男生昨提堂後，另一批 7 男 1 女，包括兩名 14 歲學生，被控在公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為、襲警等罪，今（31日）於粉嶺裁判法院提堂，其中一名被告為持雙程證的內地廣東的大學生。據悉他與其他被告被指將單張攝入萬寧店內；而 14 歲女生則被指管有鐵鎚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攝單張都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n集思廣益點幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返到鄉下唔入集中營都莫需有坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c39d5798121cfad891b6ecafb52e1f4ae1153e9","tid":1804930,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409ab04f69f017eff6a02747cb8b0dc59965338a","tid":1804930,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"<code>德美 聯署 整合</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"579ea43a864fbacb437a647310501a3b9b4af6bb","tid":1804930,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82366f5327d2b50d867d70eeaa5328baf9384bf","tid":1804930,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"只能夠幫佢諗下去台灣"},{"pid":"dde7469bed6ee36a22b5b834992c3125d4b957e0","tid":1804930,"uid":98993,"like":1,